ing: 1 (10 ounce) can diced tomatoes with green chile peppers
1 (16 ounce) can ranch style chili beans
des: "A delicious Tex-Mex Chili even the non-cooks will enjoy. Serve with picante sauce and tortilla chips OR you can put some picante sauce right in the bowl, if you like."
ins:
In Dutch oven, over medium heat brown and drain 1 pound ground beef.
Mix in diced tomatoes, ranch style chili beans, corn with liquid, minestrone soup. Season with salt and pepper to taste.
Cover and simmer 30 minutes.
